title: Michael Zezas: Optimism Over the U.S.-EU Auto Tariffs?
description: On today's episode, With a key deadline for U.S. tariffs on EU autos now past, could European stocks outperform in 2020? Head of Public Policy Michael Zezas shares some analysis.
